        This is version 1.1 of PSYCHIC FLIGHT. PSYCHIC FLIGHT was the first
        competition intro we have ever made for a party. This intro was
        released at ASSEMBLY '94, and PSYCHIC FLIGHT won the 5th place.

        This is a minor bugfix/update version. There are still some bugs in
        this intro but they will never be fixed. This is because we're busy
        making some new INTRO's and DEMO at the moment.

        This version of PSYCHIC FLIGHT is released because of some people were
        asking for SB(pro) support with our intro. (LISEN/BRC!!)

        Fixed are  : - GUS detection crashed if there wasn't any GUS installed
                     - (minor) optimizations in several intro-parts

        New options: - Added command line options
                     - 386, EMS driver and memory detection
                     - Added an external sound-driver (our own music-system)
                       which supports:
                                        GUS
                                        SOUNDBLASTER
                                        SOUNDBLASTER 2.0
                                        SOUNDBLASTER PRO
                                        ADLIB
                                        DAC
                                        STEREO-DACS
                                        STEREO-IN-ONE
                                        PC SPEAKER

        Without the driver SPMUS.EXE, only GUS is supported.
        GUS users can delete SPMUS.EXE if they want to, but the external driver
        sounds better (less GUS clicks).

